st%20question%20commenters%20posted%20had%20less%20to%20do%20with%20printing%20and%20more%20with%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20can%20think%20about%20is%20the%20dust%20and%20dirt%20catching%20on%20the%20layers%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20wrote.%20Another%20comment%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40life_0f_dani%2Fvideo%2F7372709345756237102%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20thinking%20about%20dust%20on%20the%20wall%20ridges%2C%26quot%3B%20received%20over%2019%2C000%20likes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20interesting%20question%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20can%20come%20up%20whenever%20there's%20a%20new%20industry%20innovation.%20In%20the%20case%20of%203D%20printed%20homes%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bridges%26quot%3B%20refer%20to%20the%20horizontal%20layers%20of%20material%20that%20are%20left%20behind%20after%20the%20massive%20printing%20machine%20finishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20set%20out%20to%20answer%20the%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Icon%203D%20printed%20model%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667f2d6c50b021b5caeaad57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Icon%203D%20printed%20model%20home.%3Cp%3EIcon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20four%203D%20construction%20printing%20companies%20about%20how%20to%20clean%20their%20walls.%20And%20the%20answer%20will%20have%20dust%20worriers%20rest%20assured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20from%20Icon%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bdust%20has%20not%20been%20a%20concern%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20residents%20who%20have%20lived%20in%20these%20printed%20homes%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20cleaning%2C%20you'd%20treat%20it%20similarly%20to%20any%20painted%20wall%2C%20stone%20or%20brick%20wall%2C%20and%20as%20necessary%2C%20use%20a%20dust%20cloth%20or%20damp%20microfiber%20cloth%20to%20remove%20any%20dust%20and%20debris%20by%20wiping%20clean%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniella%20Glaeze%2C%20who%20currently%20lives%20in%20one%20of%20Icon's%203D%20printed%20homes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3d-printed-home-tour-neighborhood-texas-tiktok-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20Insider%20that%20she%20hasn't%20had%20any%20trouble%20with%20grime%20collecting%20in%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ridges%20on%20the%20wall%20are%20not%20like%20little%20shelves%2C%20they're%20very%20thin%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20dust%20were%20to%20collect%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it'd%20be%20very%20noticeable%2C%20and%20the%20walls%20are%20very%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20honestly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDetroit-based%20nonprofit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3d-printed-home-224-500-detroit-see-inside-2024-3%23in-january-detroit-welcomed-its-first-concrete-3-d-printed-abode-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitizen%20Robotics%3C%2Fa%3E%20similarly%20told%20BI%20that%20its%20printed%20walls%20%26quot%3Bcan%20be%20dusted%20like%20any%20other%20surface.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%223D%20printed%20wall%20by%20nonprofit%203D%20printing%20construction%20company%20Citizen%20Robotics.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a2b371aab37011780aa45c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECitizen%20Robotics%20offers%20two%203D%20printed%20feature%20walls.%3Cp%3ECitizen%20Robotics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Danish%20startup%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-european-startup-built-a-3d-printed-concrete-home-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3DCP%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20cleaning%20measures%20for%20their%20homes%20depend%20on%20the%20type%20of%20post-treatment%20of%20their%20walls.%20CEO%20Mikkel%20Brick%20told%20BI%20that%20if%20%26quot%3Bthe%20walls%20are%20raw%2C%20you%20would%20need%20to%20vacuum%20them%20once%20in%20a%20while%20to%20combat%20the%20dust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalls%20that%20have%20received%20a%20dust%20binder%20treatment%20or%20have%20been%20polished%20do%20not%20require%20additional%20action%20to%20maintain%20them%2C%20Brick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20still%20concerned%20with%20potential%20dust-riddled%20ridges%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20people%20who%20just%20aren't%20fans%20of%20the%20aesthetic%20%E2%80%94%20some%20homes%20do%20not%20have%20the%20layers%20showcased%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMighty%20Buildings%2C%20a%203D%20printing%20company%20based%20in%20Oakland%2C%20California%2C%203D%20prints%20its%20panels%20in%20factories%20rather%20than%20on-site%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mightybuildings.com%2Fproduct%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20printed%20walls%20is%20covered%20with%20PU%20foam%20insulation%20and%20a%20steel%20frame%20and%20then%20finished%20with%20primer%20and%20paint.%20This%20means%20that%20only%20the%20exterior%20has%20the%20classic%20printed%20texture%20on%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20particular%20method%20for%20fabrication%20means%20that%20the%20interiors%20are%20finished%20in%20a%20more%20typical%20fashion%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20there's%20no%20difference%20in%20how%20you'd%20clean%20a%20regular%20wall%20and%20one%20of%20our%20walls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Citizen%20Robotics%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20company%20actually%20drywalls%20most%20of%20its%20walls%20and%20only%20has%20two%203D%20printed%20feature%20walls%20with%20exposed%20layer