Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20in%20August%202021.%20The%20certificate%2C%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%2C%20underlines%20that%20the%20basement%20is%20for%20parking%20use%20and%20household%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coaching%20centre%20for%20civil%20service%20aspirants%20got%20an%20NOC%20from%20the%20fire%20department%20earlier%20this%20month.%20This%20document%2C%20also%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%2C%20mentions%20that%20the%20building%20has%20complied%20with%20fire%20safety%20requirements.%20It%20adds%20that%20the%20basement%20should%20be%20used%20strictly%20as%20per%20building%20bye-laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20building%20bye-laws%20lay%20down%20that%20adequate%20arrangement%20shall%20be%20made%20to%20ensure%20surface%20drainage%20does%20not%20enter%20the%20basement.%20It%20also%20added%20that%20if%20the%20basement%20is%20used%20for%20office%20and%20commercial%20purposes%2C%20there%20should%20be%20a%20sufficient%20number%20of%20exit%20ways%20and%20access%20ways.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20coaching%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20entry%2Fexit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20civil%20service%20aspirants%20--%20Tania%20Soni%20and%20Shreya%20Yadav%2C%20both%2025%2C%20and%20Navin%20Delvin%2C%2028%20--%20died%20after%20heavy%20rain%20in%20Delhi%20yesterday%20led%20to%20the%20flooding%20of%20the%20basement.%20Several%20students%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20coaching%20institute's%20library%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20mayor%20Shelly%20Oberoi%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20incident%20to%20find%20out%20if%20any%20MCD%20officer%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20negligence%20that%20led%20to%20the%20tragedy.%20She%20has%20also%20said%20all%20coaching%20centres%20that%20have%20violated%20the%20law%20would%20face%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20multiple%20sections%2C%20including%20charges%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20and%20death%20due%20to%20ne