%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-group-to-commission-first-phase-of-4-bn-petchem-project-by-dec-2026-124072800125_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-group-to-commission-first-phase-of-4-bn-petchem-project-by-dec-2026-124072800125_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deaths%20In%20Flooded%20Coaching%20Basement%3A%20What%20We%20Know%20So%20Far%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20three%20students%20in%20the%20flooded%20basement%20of%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20West%20Delhi%20has%20sparked%20protests%20by%20civil%20service%20aspirants.%20Their%20bodies%20were%20recovered%20by%20rescuers%20late%20in%20the%20evening.%20The%20three%20victims%2C%20who%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Tania%20Soni%2C%2025%2C%20Shreya%20Yadav%2C%2025%2C%20and%20Navin%20Delvin%2C%2028%2C%20were%20preparing%20for%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20we%20know%20so%20far%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Tragedy%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deaths%20occurred%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20in%20old%20Rajinder%20Nagar.%20The%20basement%20has%20a%20library%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20150%2C%20and%20at%20least%2020%20children%20were%20there%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basement%20was%20flooded%20after%20heavy%20rain%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%20The%20wall%20of%20a%20drain%20in%20the%20basement%20exploded%20and%20floodwater%20started%20filling%20the%20basement%20faster.%20The%20students%20started%20evacuating%20through%20the%20only%20exit%20that%20was%20in%20the%20library.%20While%20most%20of%20them%20could%20be%20rescued%2C%20the%20three%20victims%20got%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20reports%20that%20access%20to%20the%20basement%20was%20regulated%20by%20biometric%20authentication%2C%20which%20stopped%20working%20due%20to%20a%20power%20cut%20and%20trapped%20the%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpot%20visuals%20showed%20last%20evening%20the%20basement%20completely%20flooded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescuers%20recovered%20the%20bodies%20of%20two%20students%20-%20both%20women%20-%20in%20the%20evening.%20The%20body%20of%20another%20student%20-%20a%20man%20-%20was%20found%20later%20into%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20and%20their%20bodies%20sent%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20further%20legal%20action.%20While%20Shreya%20belonged%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Tania%20was%20from%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Navin%20was%20from%20Ernakulam%2C%20Kerala%2C%20said%20the%20police.%20The%20police%20also%20requested%20the%20students%20not%20to%20gather%20at%20the%20spot%20since%20it%20may%20hamper%20the%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deaths%20have%20sparked%20a%20massive%20protest%20by%20students%20who%20allege%20negligence%20by%20civic%20authorities%20led%20to%20the%20deaths.%20Paramilitary%20forces%20have%20been%20called%20in%20to%20keep%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20is%20the%20situation%20after%2030%20minutes%20of%20rain%2C%20who%20is%20responsible%3F%20No%20one%20has%20come%20to%20talk%20to%20us%20or%20given%20us%20any%20assurance.%20Who%20will%20fix%20responsibility%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20protester.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20other%20students%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20MCD%20and%20the%20institute's%20director%20were%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20culprits%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20criminal%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20cops%20and%20two%20people%20have%20been%20detained%20for%20questioning.%20Forensic%20teams%20have%20also%20inspected%20the%20basement%20where%20the%20deaths%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Blame%20Game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20AAP%20government%20over%20the%20deaths%20and%20said%20the%20tragedy%20could%20have%20been%20avoided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBansuri%20Swaraj%2C%20BJP%20MP%20from%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20said%20BJP%20workers%20had%20repeatedly%20asked%20local%20MLA%20Durgesh%20Pathak%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20sewers%20in%20this%20area%20are%20cleaned%20and%20de-silted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that%20had%20been%20done%2C%20this%20tragedy%20would%20not%20have%20happened...the%20AAP%20government%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20and%20MLA%20Durgesh%20Pathak%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20tragedy%20and%20the%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20charges%2C%20Mr%20Pathak%20said%20the%20BJP's%20councillors%20were%20in%20power%20in%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20for%2015%20years%20but%20did%20not%20get%20drains%20constructed.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20time%20for%20politics.%20The%20focus%20now%20is%20on%20saving%20the%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MLA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722147780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fhn7hp6lo_delhi-basement-deaths-ani_625x300_28_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeaths-in-flooded-coaching-basement-what-we-know-so-far-6205991%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20death%20of%20three%20students%20in%20the%20flooded%20basement%20of%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20West%20Delhi%20has%20sparked%20protests%20by%20civil%20service%20aspirants.%20Their%20bodies%20were%20recovered%20by%20rescuers%20late%20in%20the%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeaths-in-flooded-coaching-basement-what-we-know-so-far-6205991%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2