rol%20as%20the%20students%20accuse%20municipal%20authorities%20of%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragic%20incident%20occurred%20at%20a%20building%20in%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20that%20houses%20a%20branch%20of%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%2C%20a%20prominent%20coaching%20institute%20for%20civil%20service%20aspirants.%20The%20institute's%20library%20was%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20building%2C%20and%20there%20was%20only%20one%20entry-exit.%20This%20basement%20was%20flooded%20following%20a%20downpour%20yesterday.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20there%20were%20at%20least%2020%20students%20in%20the%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Central)%20M%20Harshavardhan%20said%20a%20criminal%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20in%20this%20connection.%20%26quot%3BOur%20forensic%20teams%20are%20here.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20a%20proper%20investigation%20and%20finding%20the%20truth.%20Two%20people%20have%20been%20detained%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNDRF%20has%20recovered%20three%20bodies%20till%20now.%20One%20final%20round%20of%20search%20is%20on.%20Three%20students%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20hospital%20and%2013-14%20others%20were%20rescued%20and%20are%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Multiple%20charges%2C%20including%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20and%20causing%20death%20by%20negligence%2C%20have%20been%20invoked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20students%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20hit%20out%20at%20civic%20authorities.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20is%20the%20situation%20after%2030%20minutes%20of%20rain%2C%20who%20is%20responsible%3F%20No%20one%20has%20come%20to%20talk%20to%20us%20or%20given%20us%20any%20assurance.%20Who%20will%20fix%20responsibility%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20protester%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20students%20alleged%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20culprits%26quot%3B%20are%20MCD%20and%20the%20institute's%20director.%20%26quot%3BMCD%20calls%20it%20a%20disaster%2C%20but%20I%20say%20this%20is%20negligence.%20Knee-deep%20water%20gathers%20in%20half%20an%20hour%20of%20rain%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20student%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Tania%20Soni%2C%20Shreya%20Yadav%2C%20both%2025%2C%20and%20Navin%20Delvin%2C%2028.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Mayor%20Shelly%20Oberoi%20has%20termed%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bvery%20shocking%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20requires%20a%20%26quot%3Bthorough%20investigation%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bswift%20and%20strongest%20possible%20action%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20ordered%20action%20against%20all%20coaching%20centres%20under%20MCD%20that%20are%20running%20commercial%20activities%20in%20basements%20in%20violation%20of%20laws.%20She%20has%20also%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20to%20identify%20if%20any%20officer%20of%20MCD%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20tragedy%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20in%20Delhi%20that%20also%20controls%20the%20MCD.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20government%20and%20municipal%20corporation.%20This%20is%20the%20most%20insensitive%20government%20ever%20in%20this%20country.%20This%20is%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Manjinder%20Singh%20Sirsa%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20Delhi%20Minister%20Atishi%20and%20local%20MLA%20Durgesh%20Pathak.%20Delhi%20BJP%20chief%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Pathak%20ignored%20repeated%20appeals%20by%20local%20residents%20to%20get%20drains%20cleaned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20Government's%20criminal%20negligence%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%20mishap.%20Jal%20Board%20Minister%20Atishi%20and%20local%20MLA%20Durgesh%20Pathak%20should%20take%20responsibility%20and%20resign%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C