2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F07%2F27%2Fus-news%2Finternets-most-notorious-astrologer-who-predicted-bidens-exit-reveals-next-president%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20enjoying%20the%20height%20of%20his%20professional%20success.%20Ms%20Tripp%20argues%20that%20the%20former%20President%C2%A0might%20be%20in%20for%20more%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%20things%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20considering%20that%20he%20was%20already%20the%20target%20of%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BUranus%20is%20on%20his%20mid-heaven%20which%20shows%20...%20unpredictability%20with%20his%20career%20and%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040-year-old%20astrologer%20went%20viral%20for%20accurately%20predicting%20when%20the%2081-year-old%20Joe%20Biden%20would%20abandon%20his%20presidential%20ambitions.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Biden%20is%20made%20to%20step%20down%20it%20will%20be%20at%20the%20Capricorn%20Full%20Moon%20at%2029%20degrees%20Capricorn.%20Capricorn%20rules%20the%20government%20and%20old%20age.%2029%20degrees%20is%20an%20ending%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20July%2011.%20When%20an%20X%20user%20questioned%20her%20about%20the%20precise%20date%2C%20she%20replied%20%26quot%3BJuly%2021.%26quot%3B%20The%20woman%20predicted%20Mr%20Biden's%20departure%20since%20it%20was%20a%20full%20moon%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Tripp%20also%20foretold%20that%20Kamala%20Harris%20would%20run%20for%20US%20President%20in%202024.%20Citing%20the%20reason%2C%20she%20said%2C%20Mr%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bis%20too%20old.%26quot%3B%20She%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20she%20felt%20the%20Vice%20President%20would%20win%20the%20nomination%20since%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bexperiencing%20her%20second%20Saturn%20return.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20time%20when%20if%20you've%20been%20putting%20in%20the%20work%20since%20the%20first%20Saturn%20return%20at%2030%20you're%20rewarded%20...%20usually%20there's%20a%20(professional)%20advancement%20or%20you%20gain%20authority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20astrologer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20she%20added%20that%20Mr%20Biden%20could%20experience%20more%20difficulties%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20%26quot%3BPluto%20is%20on%20his%20sun.%20He%20could%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20health%20crisis%20come%20up%20or%20his%20health%20could%20continue%20to%20decline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Tripp%20also%20predicted%20that%20the%20month%20of%20August%20in%20the%20US%20may%20be%20difficult%20and%20that%20there%20may%20be%20more%20political%20unrest%20ahead.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Convention%20is%20set%20to%20start%20on%20August%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20recent%20surveys%20show%20that%20US%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20who%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20unseat%20Joe%20Biden%20as%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20contender%20for%20the%20presidential%20election%20on%20November%205%2C%20is%20closing%20the%20gap%20with%20Donald%20Trump.%20Support%20for%20her%20has%20significantly%20increased%20both%20inside%20her%20party%20and%20among%20non-white%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20two-person%20race%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20and%20Mr%20Trump%20are%20tied%20at%2049%25%20to%2047%25%20according%20to%20the%20most%20recent%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20survey.%20However%2C%20the%20report%20states%20this%20was%20within%20the%20margin%20of%20error%20of%20plus%20or%20minus%203.1%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722133080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F0lg1p75g_starheal_625x300_28_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fastrologer-who-correctly-predicted-biden-exit-reveals-name-of-next-us-president-6205158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Tripp%20argues%20that%20the%20former%20President%20might%20be%20in