The%20police%20cracked%20the%20case%20and%20detained%20the%20victim's%2013-year-old%20brother%2C%20their%20mother%20and%20sisters%20aged%2017%20and%2018%20after%20interrogation%20of%2050%20people%2C%20intense%20questioning%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%20and%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20technical%20evidence%2C%20he%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20details%20of%20the%20case%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Vivek%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20nine-year-old%20girl%20was%20raped%20and%20strangulated%20to%20death%20under%20Jawa%20police%20station%20limits%20on%20April%2024%2C%20following%20which%20the%20police%20had%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20started%20a%20probe.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20body%20of%20the%20victim%20was%20recovered%20from%20the%20courtyard%20of%20her%20house%20where%20she%20was%20sleeping%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20intense%20interrogation%20of%20the%20family%20members%2C%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20the%20victim's%2013-year-old%20brother%20had%20slept%20beside%20her%20at%20night.%20It%20was%20found%20that%20the%20teenage%20boy%20raped%20his%20sister%20after%20watching%20obscene%20videos%20on%20the%20mobile%20phone%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20victim%20threatened%20to%20tell%20this%20to%20their%20father%2C%20the%20boy%20stranguled%20her%20and%20later%20woke%20up%20his%20mother%20and%20confided%20in%20his%20mother.%20She%20then%20found%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20still%20alive.%20On%20seeing%20that%2C%20the%20accused%20again%20strangled%20her%2C%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20his%20two%20elder%20sisters%20also%20woke%20up%20and%20all%20of%20them%20changed%20the%20spot%20of%20their%20bed%20before%20informing%20the%20police%20to%20mislead%20the%20probe.%20However%2C%20they%20finally%20admitted%20to%20their%20crime%20after%20being%20repeatedly%20interrogated%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20legal%20steps%20are%20being%20taken%20after%20detaining%20the%20boy%2C%20his%20two%20sisters%20and%20their%20mother%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20received%20information%20on%20April%2024%20morning%20that%20the%20body%20of%20the%20girl%20was%20lying%20in%20the%20courtyard%20of%20the%20house.%20Evidence%20relating%20to%20rape%20and%20murder%20were%20found%20in%20the%20post-mortem%20report%20and%20an%20SIT%20team%20was%20constituted%20for%20the%20probe%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20mislead%20the%20investigators%2C%20the%20family%20members%20had%20told%20the%20police%20that%20the%20girl%20died%20after%20being%20bitten%20by%20a%20poisonous%20insect%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20revealed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20sign%20of%20anybody%20entering%20the%20house%2C%20and%20family%20members%20also%20denied%20hearing%20any%20sound%20during%20the%20night%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20collecting%20technical%20evidence%20and%20interrogation%20of%2050%20people%2C%20police%20found%20repeated%20changes%20in%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20family%20members.%20On%20the%20basis%20of%20suspicion%2C%20they%20were%20intensely%20interrogated%2C%20following%20which%20they%20admitted%20the%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722130800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0htt5beg_india-police-generic_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fboy-13-rapes-kills-sister-after-watching-porn-family-helps-in-cover-up-6200411%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20probing%20the%20April%2024%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%209-year-old%20girl%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Rewa%2C%20have%20found%20that%20her%20teenage%20brother%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20after%20watching%20a%20pornographic%20video%20on%20mobile%20and%20then%20killed%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%