_blank%5C%22%3Esemaglutide%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompounded%20pharmaceuticals%20are%20essentially%20copies%20of%20approved%20medications%20that%20the%20FDA%20allows%20during%20a%20shortage%20but%20which%20have%20not%20gone%20through%20the%20usual%20FDA%20approval%20process.%20This%20is%20currently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-compounded-semaglutide-online-risks-wegovy-ozempic-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20case%20for%20semaglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20sold%20under%20the%20brand%20names%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompounded%20semaglutide%20is%20a%20slightly%20more%20complex%20story%2C%20however.%20The%20Danish%20pharmaceutical%20company%20Novo%20Nordisk%20has%20a%20patent%20on%20the%20semaglutide%20molecule%20and%20doesn't%20offer%20it%20for%20sale%20for%20compounding.%20This%20has%20caused%20confusion%20over%20where%20some%20pharmacies%20are%20sourcing%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompounded%20drugs%20pose%20a%20higher%20risk%20to%20patients%20than%20FDA-approved%20drugs%20because%20compounded%20drugs%20do%20not%20undergo%20FDA%20premarket%20review%20for%20safety%2C%20quality%20or%20effectiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20alert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediet%20industry%20has%20exploded%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20part%20due%20to%20the%20FDA's%202021%20decision%20to%20approve%20semaglutide%20%E2%80%94%20a%20drug%20originally%20intended%20to%20treat%20type%202%20diabetes%20%E2%80%94%20for%20obesity%20management.%20Novo%20Nordisk's%20injectable%20medications%2C%20Wegovy%20and%20Ozempic%2C%20quickly%20gained%20attention%20from%20consumers%2C%20even%20among%20those%20who%20couldn't%20afford%20the%20steep%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20boxes%20of%20Wegovy%20on%20a%20light%20wood%20counter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad919a8ed31300199e78af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWegovy%20is%20an%20injectable%20medication%20used%20for%20weight%20loss.%3Cp%3Epicture%20alliance%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20did%20not%20share%20the%20number%20of%20reports%20it%20received%20but%20said%20the%20adverse%20health%20events%20may%20be%20related%20to%20incorrect%20dosing%20of%20compounded%20semaglutide%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDosing%20errors%20have%20resulted%20from%20patients%20measuring%20and%20self-administering%20incorrect%20doses%20of%20the%20drug%20and%20health%20care%20providers%20miscalculating%20doses%20of%20the%20drug%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FDA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20alert%20added%20that%20some%20patients%20administered%205%20to%2020%20times%20more%20than%20intended%2C%20and%20one%20healthcare%20provider%20prescribed%20at%20least%20three%20patients%2020%20units%20instead%20of%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20also%20said%20there%20are%20no%20industry%20standards%20regarding%20compounded%20semaglutide%20since%20products%20can%20come%20in%20different%20concentrations%2C%20containers%2C%20syringe%20sizes%2C%20and%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFDA%20encourages%20compounders%2C%20health%20care%20providers%2C%20and%20patients%20to%20report%20adverse%20events%20and%20medication%20errors%20associated%20with%20compounded%20semaglutide%20products%20to%20FDA's%20MedWatch%20Adverse%20Event%20Reporting%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finjectable-weight-loss-drugs-overdose-compounded-semaglutide-ozempic-wegovy-fda-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722111992000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h