le%20house%20into%20a%20Tesla%20parked%20in%20his%20yard%20as%20locals%20find%20novel%20ways%20to%20battle%20rolling%20blackouts%2C%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225070%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20charging%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3a727aab37011780ac69e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223373%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Tesla%20charging.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Keeble%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkrainians%20are%20turning%20to%20Teslas%20to%20power%20their%20homes%20amid%20rolling%20blackouts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20are%20repurposing%20old%20Tesla%20batteries%2C%20while%20others%20have%20gone%20even%20further.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20comes%20as%20the%20country%20adapts%20to%20rolling%20blackouts%20caused%20by%20Russian%20targeting%20of%20the%20energy%20grid.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainians%20are%20turning%20to%20Teslas%20to%20help%20power%20their%20homes%20and%20limit%20the%20impact%20of%20Russian%20strikes%20on%20energy%20infrastructure%2C%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F02e8e706-c15c-44aa-83fe-1a94f5d608b8%3FaccessToken%3DzwAGHir-4KW4kc8C6OcGwVxEqtOD_hqU9dYIuA.MEUCIQCWTzd8daZksm9PtWkEHg00MVGdlV1a4OyciEG5jjMDQQIgCMNuZm4O7V0W1eW5d5AFK2AKwy-3n8PpMSsGKQCHhI8%26sharetype%3Dgift%26token%3D9c7a181e-348e-404b-be5c-5219d500a7a5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Ukrainian%20businessman%20who%20is%20repurposing%20Tesla%20batteries%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20one%20Tesla%20could%20be%20used%20to%20make%20up%20to%2012%20battery%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20old%20Tesla%2C%20including%20the%20cost%20of%20delivery%2C%20will%20be%20nearly%20%2410%2C000.%20And%20you%20can%20turn%20that%20into%2012%20batteries%2C%20and%20also%20sell%20the%20parts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Oleksandr%20Bentsa%2C%20who%20had%20for%20years%20been%20buying%20crashed%20Teslas%20from%20the%20US%20and%20refitting%20and%20reselling%20them%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20five-kilowatt-hour%20(kWh)%20systems%20his%20company%20makes%20produce%20enough%20energy%20to%20power%20the%20lights%20and%20electrical%20equipment%20in%20a%20standard%20apartment%20for%2010%20hours%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Bentsa's%20novel%20idea%20may%20have%20been%20trumped%20by%20that%20of%20his%20father%2C%20who%20has%20plugged%20his%20whole%20house%20into%20a%20Tesla%20parked%20in%20his%20yard%2C%20per%20the%20FT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20100%20kWh%20battery%20can%20run%20an%20entire%20house%20for%20a%20week%2C%20Bentsa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBentsa%20told%20the%20outlet%20he%20was%20now%20expecting%20sales%20to%20boom%20as%20the%20winter%20months%20near.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20rolling%20blackouts%20are%20already%20causing%20major%20concern%20ahead%20of%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkyivindependent.com%2Fukraines-energy-supplier-ukrainians-may-have-electricity-for-6-7-hours-per-day-in-winter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKyiv%20Independent%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20energy%20supplier%20Yasno%2C%20Serhiy%20Kovalenko%2C%20said%20in%20June%20that%20locals%20may%20face%20just%20six%20or%20seven%20hours%20of%20electricity%20a%20day%20in%20winter%20if%20the%20electricity%20deficit%20is%2035%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20countries%20such%20as%20Moldova%20and%20Poland%20are%20searching%20for%20ways%20to%20help%20Ukraine%20increase%20its%20power%20supply%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20looking%20at%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20involve%20burning%20fuel%20in%20Poland%20and%20sending%20it%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20Polish%20Prime%20Minister%20Donald%20Tusk%20said%20this%20month%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%20it%20will%20partially%20help%20Ukraine%20survive%20the%20winter%2C%26quot%3B%20Tusk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20blackouts%20have%20come%20as%20the%20result%20of%20Russia's%20bombardment%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20energy%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20ramped%20up%20its%20efforts%20to%20disrupt%20the%20energy%20network%20in%20spring%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20breaking%20Ukraine's%20will%20to%20fight%20on%2C%20aiming%20particularly%20for%20energy%20generation%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeil%20Holland%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20UK's%20Delegation%20to%20the%20Organization%20for%20Security%20and%20Co-operation%20in%20Europe%20(OSCE)%2C%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20Russian%20attacks%20since%20spring%20had%20resulted%20in%20a%20total%20electricity%20loss%20of%20over%209%20GW.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-launches-mass-assault-on-ukraine-power-grid-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%26quot%3B%20attack%20on%20Ukraine's%20power%20grid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20what%20the%20Ukrainian%20energy%20ministry%20said%20was%20the%20eighth%20major%20attack%20on%20the%20country's%20energy%20infrastructure%20since%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20urgently%20need%20to%20close%20our%20skies%20or%20Ukraine%20faces%20a%20serious%20crisis%20this%20winter%2C%26quot%3B%20Maxim%20Timchenko%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20DTEK%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20energy%20company%2C%20said%20following%20the%20attack%2C%20per%20the%20BBC.%20%26quot%3BMy%20plea%20to%20allies%20is%20to%20help%20us%20defend%20our%20energy%20system%20and%20rebuild%20in%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20country's%20president%2C%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%2C%20have%20also%20pleaded%20with%20allies%20for%20increased%20air%20defense%20systems%20to%20help%20counter%20such%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Ukraine%20has%20also%20struck%20back%20at%20Russian%20energy%20sites%2C%20particularly%20targeting%20Russian%20oil%20refineries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-wont-stop-targeting-russias-oil-refineries-will-defy-us-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20urged%20Ukraine%20to%20halt%20such%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20concerns%20that%20they%20would%20cause%20a%20surge%20in%20oil%20prices%20and%20potentially%20provoke%20further%20action%20from%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%2C%20however%2C%20signaled%20that%20it%20would%20not%20stop%20such%20attacks%2C%20saying%20the%20refineries%20were%20legitimate%20military%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainians-use-tesla-batteries-power-homes-russian-attacks-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722100415000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a524c91a227600e6322e51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainians-use-tesla-batteries-power-homes-russian-attacks-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20has%20battered%20the%20Ukrainian%20energy%20grid%20in%20recent%20months%20as%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20forces%20have%20sought%20to%20break%20Ukraine's%20will%20to%20fight%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmanley%40businessinsider.com%20(Cameron%20Manley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A71%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainians-use-tesla-batteries-power-homes-russian-attacks-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20approves%20merger%20of%20Amazon%2C%20Frontizo%2C%20Appario%2C%20Haverl%3A%20All%20details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722096989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112069459%2Cimgsize-1444054.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcci-approves-proposed-combination-involving-amazon-asia-pacific-frontizo-appario-haverl-an