%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Chechen%20forces%20have%20found%20themselves%20back%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire%20since%20the%20mercenary%20Wagner%20Group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Frussia-ukraine-putin-pentagon-wagner-mercenary-prigozhin-rcna94223%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eceased%20carrying%20out%20any%20significant%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wagner%20Group%20has%20been%20effectively%20disbanded%20over%20the%20last%20year%20since%20the%20death%20of%20its%20leader%2C%20Yevgeny%20Prigozhin%2C%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarold%20Chambers%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20Russia's%20North%20Caucasus%20regions%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20with%20the%20dismantling%20of%20the%20Wagner%20group%2C%20Kadyrov's%20men%20(sometimes%20called%20Kadyrovtsy)%20were%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bstep%20in%26quot%3B%20and%20fill%20that%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20also%20taken%20a%20couple%20ex-Wagner%20commanders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20including%20some%20who%20previously%20criticized%20the%20Kadyrovtsy%20for%20their%20cowardice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2797f94-9fce-44ca-a837-7a2c853844e7%5C%22%3ESome%20Russian%20soldiers%20receive%20just%20up%20to%2010%20days%20of%20training%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20providing%20personnel%2C%20Chechnya%20is%20also%20helping%20train%20Russian%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MoD%20said%20in%20May%20that%20the%20Russian%20Special%20Forces%20(Spetznaz)%20University%20in%20Gudermes%2C%20Chechnya%2C%20had%20trained%20around%2042%2C000%20Russian%20troops%20since%202022%20%E2%80%94%20citing%20figures%20from%20Chechnya's%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MoD%20said%20that%20trainees%20receive%20only%20up%20to%2010%20days%20of%20training%20at%20the%20university%2C%20%26quot%3Bbringing%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20training%