2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPurple's%20responsive%20%26quot%3BGelFlex%26quot%3B%20grid%20sets%20it%20apart%20from%20other%20brands.%20The%20PurpleFlex's%20polymer%20grid%20is%20two%20inches%20thick%20and%20comprises%20the%20top%20layer%20of%20the%20mattress.%20The%20grid%20reminds%20me%20of%20a%20honeycomb%20with%20squares%20instead%20of%20hexagons.%20It%20has%20an%20open%20structure%20to%20allow%20for%20airflow%2C%20and%20it's%20hyper-elastic%2C%20so%20it%20squishes%20when%20you%20lie%20on%20it%20and%20quickly%20rebounds%20when%20you%20get%20up.%20The%20grid%20is%20surrounded%20by%20a%20foam%20border%20for%20increased%20edge%20support.%20The%20six-inch%20high-density%20base%20foam%20offers%20durability%20and%20support.%20The%20soft%20polyester%20cover%20is%20designed%20for%20breathability%20and%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20foams%20used%20in%20the%20mattress%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcertipur.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECertiPUR-US%20certified%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20PurpleFlex%20is%20also%20made%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.intertek.com%2Fcertification%2Findoor-air-quality%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClean%20Air%20Gold-certified%3C%2Fa%3E%20materials%2C%20meaning%20it%20has%20low%20VOC%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20PurpleFlex%20Mattress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Setup%5C%22%3ESetup%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PurpleFlex%20arrives%20at%20your%20door%20in%20a%20box%20the%20size%20of%20a%20minifridge.%20The%20queen%20mattress%20weighs%2077%20pounds%20%E2%80%94%20more%20in%20the%20packaging%20%E2%80%94%20so%20have%20someone%20to%20help%20you%20move%20it%20to%20your%20bedroom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20the%20PurpleFlex%20was%20pretty%20standard%2C%20but%20it%20comes%20with%20instructions%2C%20a%20cutting%20tool%20for%20removing%20the%20plastic%2C%20and%20sleep%20masks%2C%20which%20my%2010-year-old%20loves%20to%20wear%20all%20day.%20To%20set%20it%20up%2C%20you%20empty%20the%20vacuum-sealed%20mattress%20onto%20your%20foundation.%20Then%2C%20remove%20the%20plastic%20layers%2C%20being%20careful%20not%20to%20cut%20into%20the%20mattress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20to%20set%20up%20mattresses%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20give%20them%20time%20to%20expand%20and%20air%20out%20by%20bedtime.%20The%20PurpleFlex%20had%20a%20mild%20%26quot%3Bnew%20bed%20smell%26quot%3B%20when%20I%20first%20unboxed%20it%2C%20but%20it%20dissipated%20by%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20set%20up%20your%20mattress%20yourself%2C%20Purple%20offers%20in-home%20setup%20for%20%24200.%20They'll%20even%20take%20the%20packaging%20with%20them%20and%20remove%20your%20old%20mattress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comfort%20and%20support%5C%22%3EComfort%20and%20support%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221245%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shirtless%20man%20lies%20on%20a%20mattress%20with%20his%20back%20to%20the%20camera%20and%20with%20spine%20aligning%20dots%20overlaid%20on%20the%20photo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ea4f8fb2b6bedb0594c5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22622%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20measured%20deviation%20angle%20of%20six%20degrees%20or%20less%20is%20considered%20good.%20The%20PurpleFlex%20was%20excellent.%3Cp%3EMattress%20Checker%20app%3B%20James%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20polymer%20grid%20layer%20responds%20to%20your%20body's%20contours%20the%20moment%20you%20lay%20on%20it.%20I%20could%20feel%20my%20pressure%20points%20squishing%20the%20grid%20and%20reaching%20the%20base%20foam%2C%20which%20helped%20me%20feel%20supported%20and%20kept%20my%20spine%20optimally%20aligned.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20PurpleFlex%20has%20the%20best%20spinal%20alignment%20of%20any%20mattress%20I've%20tested.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fmattress-checker%2Fid959223688%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMattress%20Checker%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20spine%20was%20off%20from%20being%20perfectly%20aligned%20by%201.7%20degrees.%20Anything%20below%206%20degrees%20is%20considered%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20heavy%20guy%20who%20sleeps%20on%20his%20side%2C%20and%20I%20found%20the%20mattress%20was%20a%20tinge%20too%20firm%20for%20my%20tastes.%20Based%20on%20testing%2090%2B%20mattresses%2C%20I'd%20say%20it's%20a%20little%20firmer%20than%20average%2C%20making%20it%20better%20suited%20for%20back%20and%20stomach%20sleepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20didn't%20wake%20up%20feeling%20sore.%20According%20to%20my%20Garmin%20Forerunner%20945%20watch%2C%20my%20sleep%20quality%20was%20average%20while%20testing%20the%20PurpleFlex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Heat%20dissipation%5C%22%3EHeat%20dissipation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20test%20how%20cool%20a%20mattress%20stays%20and%20how%20well%20it%20dissipates%20heat%20by%20measuring%20its%20surface%20temperature%20right%20before%20I%20lie%20down%2C%20right%20after%20I%20get%20up%2C%20and%20two%20minutes%20after.%20Over%20the%20two-to-four-week%20testing%20period%2C%20I%20take%20several%20measurements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PurpleFlex%20was%20among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-mattress%5C%22%3Ebest%20cooling%20mattresses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20I%20got%20up%20from%20it%2C%20it%20was%2C%20on%20average%2C%2087.5%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20two%20degrees%20less%20than%20the%20average%20of%20all%20the%20beds%20I've%20tested.%20However%2C%20it%20didn't%20dissipate%20heat%20quickly.%20After%20two%20minutes%2C%20the%20temperature%20only%20dropped%208.5%20degrees%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20average%20of%2012%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubjectively%2C%20I%20never%20overheated%20on%20the%20PurpleFlex%2C%20even%