20and%20biological%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20creating%20a%20self-sustained%20farm%2C%20the%20next%20step%20was%20to%20create%20a%20market%20for%20the%20products.%20For%20this%2C%20Krishnasudha%20stepped%20in%20and%20suggested%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356941%2Forganic-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores-earthy-tales-delhi-ncr-deepak-sabharwal-rajasthan-farm-pesticides%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue-added%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20coconut%20oil%20and%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20set%20up%20a%20production%20unit%20on%20their%20farm%20itself%20with%20a%20solar%20dryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%20has%20been%20a%20learning%20experience%20here.%20There%20is%20lesser%20stress%20as%20compared%20to%20a%20corporate%20job%20with%20the%20added%20benefit%20of%20serving%20good%20products%20to%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Deesan%20Farms%20makes%20a%20tonne%20of%20coconut%20oil%20and%20250%20kg%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghee%20%3C%2Fem%3Eper%20week%2C%20claims%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGetting%20youngsters%20interested%20in%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Saravanan%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20about%20farming%20thanks%20to%20his%20parents%20and%20grandparents%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20natural%20farming%20course.%20He%20says%20that%20this%20helped%20him%20with%20better%20ways%20of%20creating%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-17