ng%20in%20value%20addition.%20He%20also%20implemented%20a%20solar%20dryer%20for%20post-harvest%20management.%20Students%20and%20farmers%20from%20across%20South%20India%20visit%20his%20farm%20to%20attend%20his%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sreedhu%2C%20adding%20that%20more%20youngsters%20must%20consider%20this%20path%20instead%20of%20running%20to%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20facing%20a%20nutritional%20crisis%20today%20due%20to%20the%20food%20that%20is%20grown%20and%20consumed.%20The%20younger%20generation%20must%20get%20into%20farming%20and%20go%20back%20to%20the%20way%20things%20were%20done%20before%20%E2%80%94%20organic%20and%20adding%20technology%20where%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20consider%20that%20while%20we%20focus%20on%20increasing%20our%20bank%20balances%20and%20securing%20our%20children%E2%80%99s%20financial%20future%2C%20we%20are%20only%20providing%20them%20with%20financial%20security.%20What%20about%20ensuring%20their%20food%20security%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Gnana%20Saravanan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721658826000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D357927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gnana%20Saravanan%20and%20Krishnasudha%2C%20IT%20professionals%20in%20Chennai%2C%20left%20their%20corporate%20jobs%20to%20return%20to%20their%20farming%20roots%20in%20Palakkad%2C%20Kerala.%20Over%20the%20past%20eight%20years%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20used%20technology%20to%20build%20a%20self-sustaining%20integrated%20farm%20called%20Deesan%20Farms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357927%2Forganic-farming-biogas-dairy-integrated-farm-self-sustaining-deesan-farms-palakkad-kerala-gnana-saravanan-krishnasudha